                <h1>Maria Ressa: Champion of Press Freedom</h1>
                <p>Maria Ressa is a celebrated journalist and co-founder of Rappler, a digital news platform in the Philippines. Known for her fearless journalism, she has been a vocal advocate for press freedom and democracy. Ressa's work in exposing the dangers of misinformation and government accountability has garnered international acclaim, including the Nobel Peace Prize in 2021.</p>
